items.name: TracingDarkWebAndBlockChain
items.description: This repository presents a detailed case study on tracking cryptocurrency transactions and uncovering dark web operations. Using open-source intelligence (OSINT) tools and blockchain forensics, we trace Bitcoin transactions, identify hidden connections between onion sites, and track funds to cryptocurrency exchanges like Binance.
